eries: Simplifying the Gulp Flow","2019-06-10 20:51:33",[12,5,14,15],"We haven't added Babel and other tools yet, but the `require` list is already getting long. Let me show how to clean it up.",{"url":43,"title":44,"date":45,"updated":3,"category":12,"tags":46,"description":47,"readingMinutes":17},"\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F10\u002Fgulp-series-06-css-minify\u002F","Gulp Series: Minifying and Optimizing CSS","2019-06-10 20:01:40",[12,5,14,15],"CSS minification was actually already added in the PostCSS chapter. This post is about distinguishing between dev and prod modes.",{"url":49,"title":50,"date":51,"updated":3,"category":12,"tags":52,"description":53,"readingMinutes":54},"\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F10\u002Fgulp-series-05-postcss\u002F","Gulp Series: Installing PostCSS","2019-06-10 16:55:17",[12,5,14,15],"New chapter — let's install PostCSS to go with the SCSS we set up earlier.","2",{"url":56,"title":57,"date":58,"updated":3,"category":12,"tags":59,"description":61,"readingMinutes":17},"\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F10\u002Fgulp-series-04-scss\u002F","Gulp Series: Installing SCSS","2019-06-10 16:18:14",[12,60,5,14,15],"SCSS","We've covered the basics. Time to add Sass\u002FSCSS handling to Gulp.",{"url":63,"title":64,"date":65,"updated":3,"category":12,"tags":66,"description":67,"readingMinutes":17},"\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F10\u002Fgulp-series-03-basics\u002F","Gulp Series: Basic Gulp","2019-06-10 10:52:26",[12,5,14,15],"Environment, project folder, and Gulp are all set up. Time to write some basic Gulp.",{"url":69,"title":70,"date":71,"updated":3,"category":12,"tags":72,"description":73,"readingMinutes":54},"\u002Fen\u002Fgulp\u002F2019\u002F06\u002F10\u002Fgulp-series-02-install\u002F","Gulp Series: Installing Gulp","2019-06-10 10:09:08",[12,5,14,15],"Last post got us familiar with what Gulp is. This one walks through installing Gulp from scratch. Keep your terminal open — we'll be using it a lot.",1